        <num>5</num>
        <heading>Director of the authorities budget office</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_5__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of subdivision one of section one hundred\nsixty-nine of the executive law. The director may be removed by the\ngovernor only after notice and opportunity to be heard, and only for:\n  1. permanent disability;\n  2. inefficiency;\n  3. neglect of duty;\n  4. malfeasance;\n  5. a felony or conduct involving moral turpitude; or\n  6. breach of fiduciary duty.\n</p>
          </content>
